what_failed: Regression (0.80x): Replaced the comma join (cross join) with reason by materializing filtered returns first, then left joining to store_sales. This isolates the dimension table filter into a CTE and avoids the Cartesian product pattern.
why_it_failed: Converted a correlated LEFT JOIN + filter into two materialized CTEs (sales_with_filtered_returns AND filtered_returns), both scanning store_returns. The original correlated LEFT JOIN was efficiently executed as a semi-join during the store_sales scan. Materializing both CTEs forces independent scans and loses the semi-join optimization.
